00402022933/https://interaktiv.tagesspiegel.de/lab/karte-sars-cov-2-in-deutschland-landkreise/ |archive-date=2 April 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|FRA}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in France|France]]\n|124,869\n|13,197\n|24,932\n|<ref>{{Cite web| https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/country/france/|url=https://www.santepubliquefrance.fr/maladies-et-traumatismes/maladies-et-infections-respiratoires/infection-a-coronavirus/articles/infection-au-nouveau-coronavirus-sars-cov-2-covid-19-france-et-monde |title=Infection au nouveau Coronavirus (SARS-CoV-2), COVID-19, France et Monde |website=www.santepubliquefrance.fr |language=fr |access-date=11 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321143945/https://www.santepubliquefrance.fr/maladies-et-traumatismes/maladies-et-infections-respiratoires/infection-a-coronavirus/articles/infection-au-nouveau-coronavirus-sars-cov-2-covid-19-france-et-monde |archive-date=21 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|UK}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the United Kingdom|United Kingdom]]\n|73,758\n|8,958\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.arcgis.com/apps/opsdashboard/index.html#/f94c3c90da5b4e9f9a0b19484dd4bb14 |title=Total UK COVID-19 Cases Update |publisher=Public Health England |access-date=9 April 2020 |archive-url=http://archive.is/Rlug5 |archive-date=9 April 2020|url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|TUR}} <!---deleting from Europe will be considered vandalism and will lead to blocking of account and IP---> [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Turkey|Turkey]]\n|47,029\n|1,006\n|2,423\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://covid19.tubitak.gov.tr/turkiyede-durum |title=T\u00fcrkiye'de Durum |website=covid19.tubitak.gov.tr/ |access-date=27 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326162202/https://covid19.tubitak.gov.tr/turkiyede-durum |archive-date=26 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|BEL}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Belgium|Belgium]]\n|26,667\n|3,019\n|