/corona-viruset/ |title=Live-oppdatering: coronavirusets spredning i Norge og verden |last=Nilsen |first=Av Sondre |last2=Skjetne |first2=Oda Leraan |website=VG Nett |access-date=11 March 2020 |last3=Sfrintzeris |first3=Yasmin |last4=R\u00f8set |first4=Hanna Haug |last5=breaking-avdeling |first5=Carina Hunshamar og VGs |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320002130/https://www.vg.no/spesial/2020/corona-viruset/ |archive-date=20 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name=\"VG\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.vg.no/spesial/2020/corona/ |title=Corona-viruset: Slik spres viruset i Norge og verden. Kart og statistikk |publisher=Vg.no |access-date=2020-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329020316/https://www.vg.no/spesial/2020/corona/ |archive-date=29 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|POL}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Poland|Poland]]\n|5,955\n|181\n|318\n|<ref name=\"Poland_stats_10april\">{{Cite news |url=https://twitter.com/MZ_GOV_PL/status/1248627562349088768 |title=(Tweet) |date=10 April 2020 |access-date=10 April 2020 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/zIKy5 |archive-date=10 April 2020 |quote=[5955/181 (total lab-confirmed/total deaths)] |website=Twitter }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|DNK}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Denmark|Denmark]]\n|5,819\n|247\n|1,773\n|<ref name=\"STPS numbers\" />\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|CZE}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the Czech Republic|Czech Republic]]\n|5,674\n|119\n|346\n|<ref name=\"CZE\">{{Cite web |url=https://onemocneni-aktualne.mzcr.cz/covid-19 |title=P\u0159ehled situace v \u010cR: COVID-19 |date=27 March 2020 |website=mzcr.cz |language=cs |url-status=live |access-date=27 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322121846/https://onemocneni-aktualne.mzcr.cz/covid-19 |archive-date=22 March 2020 }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|ROU}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Romania|Romania]]\n|5,467\n|257\n|729\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/i