]])\n* {{flagicon|Germany}} [[Lothar Emmerich]] ([[Striker (association football)|FW]])\n* {{flagicon|Germany}} [[Michael Glowatzky]] ([[Striker (association football)|FW]])\n* {{flagicon|Germany}} [[Sebastian Knei\u00dfl]] ([[Midfielder|MF]])\n* {{flagicon|Germany}} [[Florian Trinks]] ([[Midfielder|MF]])\n\n===International caps===\n'''[[Germany national football team]]''' ([[Cap (sports)|Caps]]/Goals):\n* {{flagicon|Germany}} Albin Kitzinger: [[List of Germany international footballers|44/2]]\n* {{flagicon|Germany}} Andreas Kupfer: [[List of Germany international footballers|44/1]]\n* {{flagicon|Germany}} G\u00fcnter Bernard: [[List of Germany international footballers|2/0]] (3 additional caps for [[SV Werder Bremen]])\n'''[[Europe XI]]''' (Caps/Goals):\n* {{flagicon|Germany}} Albin Kitzinger: 1/0\n* {{flagicon|Germany}} Andreas Kupfer: 1/0\n\n==Non-playing staff==\n===Current management team===\n{{updated|21 February 2020}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Name\n! Position\n! Source\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Coaching staff\n|-\n| {{flagicon|GER}} Tobias Strobl\n| Head coach\n|<ref name=\"Staff\"/>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|GER}} Jan Gernlein\n| Assistant coach\n|<ref name=\"Staff\"/>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|GER}} Norbert Kleider\n| Goalkeeping coach\n|<ref name=\"Staff\"/>\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Athletic department\n|-\n| {{flagicon|GER}} Christian Hasler\n| Athletic coach\n|<ref name=\"Staff\"/>\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Medical department\n|-\n| {{flagicon|GER}} Dr. Matthias Blanke\n| First team doctor\n|<ref name=\"Staff\"/>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|GER}} Arben Krasniqi\n| Rehabilitation coach\n|<ref name=\"Staff\"/>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|GER}} Thomas Reinl\n| Rehabilitation coach\n|<ref name=\"Staff\"/>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|GER}} Daniel Lommel\n| Rehabilitation coach\n|<ref name=\"Staff\"/>\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Organisation and management\n|-\n| ''currently vacant''\n| Director of football\n|<ref name=\"Staff\"/>\n|}\n\n===Managerial history===\nHead coaches of the club from 1929:<ref>{{cite web|title=1. FC Schweinfurt 05: Trainerhistorie|publisher=www.weltfussball.de|url=http://www.weltfussball.de/teams/1-fc-schweinfurt-05/9/|accessdate=17 June 2017|language=German}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=1. FC Schweinfurt 05: Die Trainer|trans-title=1. FC Schweinfurt 05: Managers|publisher=www.mainpost.de|url=https://m.mainpost.de/sport/schweinfurt/Die-Trainer;art795,3080687|accessdate=29 July 2019|language=German}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" \n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#dfdfdf\"\n| '''Manager'''\n| '''Start'''\n| '''Finish'''\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Karl Willnecker\n| 1 July 1929\n| 30 June 1930\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Hans Teufel\n| 1 July 1930\n| 30 June 1933\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} [[Leonhard Seiderer]]\n| 1 July 1933\n| 30 June 1934\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Fritz Benn\u00f6der\n| 1 July 1934\n| 30 June 1935\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Hans Teufel\n| 1 July 1935\n| 30 April 1936\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Hans Sauerwein\n| 1 May 1936\n| 30 April 1938\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Ludwig Leinberger\n| 1 May 1938\n| 30 April 1941\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Albin Kitzinger\n| 1 May 1941\n| 30 April 1946\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Hans Teufel\n| 1 May 1946\n| 30 June 1947\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Andreas Kupfer\n| 1 July 1947\n| 30 March 1949\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Erich Kratzsch\n| 1 April 1949\n| 30 June 1950\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Albin Kitzinger\n| 1 July 1950\n| 30 June 1951\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|Germany}} Kuno Kr\u00fcgel\n| 1 July 1951\n| 31 October 1951\n|- align=\"center\"\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagic